Amanda Taylor has been charged with first-degree murder in the death of her former father-in-law Charles Taylor . 
  Charles Taylor was found stabbed to death at his home in Virginia on April 4 . 
  Amanda Taylor allegedly blamed her husband Rex Taylor for introducing him to drugs at age 15 . 
  Rex Taylor hanged himself last August . 
  Police say Amanda Taylor stabbed Charles Taylor in retaliation for his suicide . 
  She also allegedly shot her alleged accomplice as the two fled police . 
  Sean Ball was found wounded on the side of a North Carolina highway . 
 